$interpreted: Law: Almost there...the odor is getting stronger.
Law: ...Oh, there's activity ahead.
Head Poacher: Everybody listen up. Stay to the path we checked out before. Today's target is 10 platypuses and 10 frogodiles.
Head Poacher: Remember! Don't let that mermaid find out!
Poacher: Boss, that mermaid's probably worth a bundle. Why don't we knock her unconscious and take her away...
Head Poacher: You want to be eager and impatient like the rest of 'em?
Head Poacher: We capture a few at a time, let them battle it out amongst themselves, that's the best plan. That mermaid's pretty tough. We'll finish her off last.
Poacher: Spoken like a true leader; didn't think of that!
Head Poacher: Only by thinking ahead can we get that fat stack. Learn a little, why don't you!?
Law: (I see, they've been covering up their smell to check out Maple Lake, looking for paths in.)
Law: (Since I found them...eh?)
Law: (Yan-Bo...why's he here?)
Law: (Indeed, ye noticed these tracks as well?)
Head Poacher: Alright, everybody listen. We'll head out on three.
Head Poacher: One!
Head Poacher: Two...
Law: (...Three.)
Poacher: Wh-What happened! All of a sudden...guys?
Head Poacher: Don't freak! Everyone settle down!
Law: Ye hast stumbled upon the wrong place, am I right Yan-Bo?
Yan-Bo: My old friend speaks the truth, he does. Return from whence you came.
Poacher: It's just two shriveled up farts. No need to fear! Slaughter them...
Head Poacher: What-What's happening...?
Law: Only ye remain. Best surrender.
Head Poacher: Hmph. You think just 'cuz you beat my men that you win?
Head Poacher: Beasts can't use Runes. I'll show you my secret Rune powers!
Law: Nowhere to run!
Yan-Bo: Wish to have a piece of Maple Lake's younglings, do you? If I let you go, eventually come back, you will.
Law: We must teach thee an unforgettable lesson. Make ye never dare return.
Law: ──This mace shall be used to teach ye the taste of fear!
Yan-Bo: Old friend, why do you involve yourself? Maple Lake business, this is. Relation to you, it has none...
Law: How couldst it bear no relation to me?
Yan-Bo: The relation, I see not.
Law: Maple Lake, as it is my old friend's new home, of course it relates to me.
Law: Have I mispoken, old friend?
Yan-Bo: ...Many thanks, old friend.
